    "description": "Double your main protein. With a few clever tweaks, a low calorie taste of BBQ is as easy as pie. To create an irresistible meal of your own, you'll serve up pulled barbecue chicken-topped cheesy chips with tomato, little gem and smokey yoghurt. Under 600 calories.",
